Program will exit.

508 servers are packaged meaning when there run/ compiled it does to the directorys and compiles. You either have your class server missing or its in the wrong place. One of your directorys must be wrong, i don’t know much about 508’s i don’t even know how to change there names, but thats my guess judging by the code.

check all your directorys are good. Also make sure your run code is actually getting to the .class files.
